observationText: The MPNST-642 cell line was recently established and is an NF1-associated MPNST cell line.

The MPNST-642 cell line was one of six MPNST cell lines used to evaluate the effects of histone deacetylase inhibitors (HDACis) on growth and clonogenicity. MPNST-642 was found to be sensitive to the HDACi PCI-24781, with a GI50 between 0.1 and 0.35 Î¼M after 48 hours of treatment.
